{
  "schema_version": 1,
  "description": "Curated drone/aerial object-detection models for dvsa-api. Weights are NOT bundled; download from source_url and place at artifact_filename, then point ModelSpec.path/labels_file at the local files (or set a base_dir when loading the catalog).",
